description: This project has been retired after migration to GitHub. Please refer to GitHub page for further details.  his project has been retired after migration to GitHub. Please refer to GitHub page for further details.  Apache Maven Artifact Resolver is a library for working with artifact repositories and dependency resolution. Maven Artifact Resolver deals with the specification of local repository, remote repository, developer workspaces, artifact transports and artifact resolution.
